-- Telefonica to Have 270 Million Latin America Clients by 2015, Alierta Says
-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 2010-11-17T09:03:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-17/telefonica-to-have-270-million-latin-america-clients-by-2015-alierta-says.html
Telefonica SA aims to have 270
million clients in Latin America by 2015, up from about 180
million now, Chairman Cesar Alierta said today at an event in
Madrid.  To contact the reporter on this story:
